As part of efforts to create massive publicity across the Niger-Delta Region, South-South Geo-political zone, and Nigeria in general, the Committee Chairman, and Special Assistant to Delta State Governor Sen. Ifeanyi Okowa on Political Matters, Comr Uyero Erarawewho, has said that the Youth Wing of People’s Democratic Party, PDP in the South-South Zone will work assiduously to mobilize and rescue Nigeria come 2023, from this present Nation’s Economic quagmire and Political failure created by APC Government. Governor Okowa’s Aide made this disclosure in a Press statement made available to newsmen in Asaba, Delta State capital as he call on all Nigerians, most importantly the people of South-South Geo-political zone to get tuned to “PEOPLE’S FM 93.1, BAYELSA by 2:20pm TOMORROW as he visits for live broadcast to sensitize the Youths of the Region. According to him, “the purpose of the summit is to call on the Youths of the Region to resist APC’s bad governance, failed propaganda, government of oppression and poverty come 2023 and vote for the People’s Democratic Party, PDP for good governance and Socio-economic development”. Community Decries Spate Of Cultism In Delta, Seeks IGP’s… Three Kidnappers Nabbed By Police After Failed Operation In… He then thanked the Youths of the Niger-Delta Region for the consistent support to the Programs of People’s Democratic, PDP in the Region.He said: “We commend the support of all our party leaders in the Region. Tomorrow’s program will definitely be a memorable day as APC’s failed promises to the citizens will be exposed”. “We will continue in our massive sensitization, mobilization of Youths across different states of the Region to work in one voice for sustainable development and victory for the party come 2023. We enjoined all our Youths to key into this finest Political ideology of our great party, PDP”.